Step 1 - Click autosacling in the left pane
Step 2 - Input details - name - switch to launch config
Step 3 - Click create a launch config
Step 4 - Input details - Name, AMI & instance type
Step 5 - Click existing security group
Step 6 - Choose an existing key pair, acknowldge - Click create
Step 7 - Successfully launch
Step 8 - Go back to the previous tab - Refresh - Select config launched
Step 9 - Click next - Go to network - subnet 1a,1b
Step 10 - Choose details as seen - existing LB, LB target group, select target group
Step 11 - Config group size and scaling policies
Step 12 - Select target tracking scaling policy, click next
Step 13 - Click add notification, create new - create topic - choose mail - next
Step 14 - Create tags and click next
Step 15 - Review and click create auto scaling group
Step 16 - Successfully created scaling policy, topic, sub, notification
Step 17 - Click instances on the left pane
Step 18 - Choose instance created - click actions - terminate instance
Step 19 - Click on load balancer on the left pane
Step 20 - Copy the link of your LB and paste in a new tab
Step 21 - View website
